A ACADEMIA DO SR. KLEKS

976
02:00:38,320 --> 02:00:40,920
{\an8}FELIZ ANIVERSÁRIO, ADA!

977
02:00:41,400 --> 02:00:42,400
{\an8}Deixa que eu atendo.

